replies.body:
Could you re-do the survey or something, I like that we have to wait years to see these champions look like they fit in with the rest of league. I know champup is working hard and I think they are doing a great job. BUT I just dont think it's fair, esp for champs like blitz and morg who's kits are honestly okay to have to wait so long.

